{"tid":2256000,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"利比亞 敍利亞等內戰國家係點生活？","createTime":"2020-10-24T04:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T13:00:46.000Z","uid":204309,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c4175783a02b899c03864665a228ec13f5f0ce77","tid":2256000,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"好似利比亞咁<br />\n呢幾年不停內戰<br />\n兩邊軍方各控制一方，仲有好多武裝分支<br />\n除左軍人外，應該都有商人同平民係果到住？<br />\n仲使唔使返學返工？<br />\n係果到拍緊拖既平民係點生活？周街都有人揸槍，會唔會見住女朋友比揸槍既武裝佬搶走，捉去姦都無得出聲？咁果到d後生女咪好唔安全？點生活"},{"pid":"295685fc76030c8aafea02a78a9ad5f4a8e92d88","tid":2256000,"uid":49119,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"非前線生活如常，耐唔時把口廢up幾句，之後好似無事發生一樣，每日ff個國家所有野仲係內戰前<br />\n個畫面係唔係好熟呢"},{"pid":"3ee430ee0f7830034447b825523668a8b64f109e","tid":2256000,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:49:08.000Z","msg":"其實非前線係無乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個國家好大"},{"pid":"c00d1145f9f29d585fc11f30a66f4584ed464509","tid":2256000,"uid":137038,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"會唔會好似旺角打緊，土瓜灣就如常生活"},{"pid":"62ad4b1171a2d4ce89f75deea82d5250fa9df701","tid":2256000,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T05:05:21.000Z","msg":"朝早俾槍聲嘈醒<br />\n<br />\n刷完牙準備出門時突然有粒炸彈炸左隔離街間屋<br />\n<br />\n眼前有幾架軍車行過，返入屋避避先<br />\n打個電話同老細講會遲到<br />\n<br />\n等左三個字，啲車聲靜左，又出門返工"},{"pid":"8ee7bd017fde9038700245925a4a9e4b0fcd5c77","tid":2256000,"uid":204309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c00d1145f9f29d585fc11f30a66f4584ed464509","tid":2256000,"uid":137038,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"會唔會好似旺角打緊，土瓜灣就如常生活"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T05:05:51.000Z","msg":"佢果d打係打到d樓爛哂<br />\n條街有屍體<br />\n無路人架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋好難保佢個戰線唔會打到去隔離<br />\n點正常生活<br />\n隨時打仗"},{"pid":"588038d92da66780b631d5648c989434927d62aa","tid":2256000,"uid":55502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:25:14.000Z","msg":"認真答你，平民走得果批早就走撚哂，<br />\n去埃及，去土耳其，水路陸路偷渡入歐，<br />\n慘絕人寰。"},{"pid":"a3e4444650768c91332b9690306de343bc402cc0","tid":2256000,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"588038d92da66780b631d5648c989434927d62aa","tid":2256000,"uid":55502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:25:14.000Z","msg":"認真答你，平民走得果批早就走撚哂，<br />\n去埃及，去土耳其，水路陸路偷渡入歐，<br />\n慘絕人寰。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"應該為數唔小架喎"},{"pid":"025874e2a9d37db54db34a6fe905a4ab9028bb83","tid":2256000,"uid":55502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3e4444650768c91332b9690306de343bc402cc0","tid":2256000,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"588038d92da66780b631d5648c989434927d62aa","tid":2256000,"uid":55502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:25:14.000Z","msg":"認真答你，平民走得果批早就走撚哂，<br />\n去埃及，去土耳其，水路陸路偷渡入歐，<br />\n慘絕人寰。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"應該為數唔小架喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:33:07.000Z","msg":"係為數唔小呀，<br />\n偷渡失敗死咗嘅多過成功偷渡嘅好多，<br />\n尤其是因為後期難民太多，<br />\n週邊國家捉得好嚴，<br />\n本身比較歡迎難民嘅埃及都泥菩薩探肛。<br />\n但係走有一線生機，<br />\n唔走，叙利亞果啲講緊唔係一對一打緊，<br />\n係六國大封相咁打，你後生行得走得，<br />\n點都捉到你入伍。"},{"pid":"7af12151d6170b01624bf9c1225b36d93d166a1a","tid":2256000,"uid":17125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"個天冧落嚟都阻唔到人類返工㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzWoz9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzWoz9p.jpg&h=aa54723d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d538aec2606645586905fbf0abfd68d68b406c5e","tid":2256000,"uid":367044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T19:10:17.000Z","msg":"冇咁亂嗰啲部份一樣返工返學<br />\nEg. Syria 嘅Rojava 入面一樣有大學 中學 政府機構 etc."},{"pid":"37b9820bfe08b24909a980e42aa3f1ecd00184a4","tid":2256000,"uid":244832,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T19:55:40.000Z","msg":"樓主有興趣可以睇《致莎瑪：敘利亞家書》記錄片， 百老匯電影中心而家上映緊"},{"pid":"770334c64e2adb2953492f3208246f8b81d50155","tid":2256000,"uid":142944,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T20:09:58.000Z","msg":"傾下點去民主國家<br />\n去到之後點逼人信佢宗教<br />\n點樣聖戰咁"},{"pid":"5c88884bb729c679e32a0865f27909880e99647f","tid":2256000,"uid":15315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T21:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7577271db3b72cb9abf40f2ded021ea541570d4e","tid":2256000,"uid":15315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c88884bb729c679e32a0865f27909880e99647f","tid":2256000,"uid":15315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T21:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T21:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcff9e1956a2c9fa78ee886469c6cd6985543129","tid":2256000,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"多謝上面各位巴打既回應<br />\n長知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦好有感概"},{"pid":"2a1cd7e4815b48e34d7e587ac0879252ea3756db","tid":2256000,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24f734c47c35c4aeeb97eb7d9af28c2a0c835a07","tid":2256000,"uid":9906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"介紹你睇一本書&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n《A Thousand Splendid Suns》<br />\n<br />\n故事係從兩個伊拉克嘅婦人嘅角度出發，由70年代寫到近代，寫佢地心路歷程、成長經過；被逼結婚後嘅家庭壓力、掙扎同矛盾。佢地兩個share一個老公，但老公係仆街嚟，屋企家暴、出面就戰亂，但個女都繼續返學。佢地曾經想走佬去伊朗但唔成功，最後係呢個被形容係有「燦爛千陽」嘅國家都係分唔開。<br />\n<br />\n入面有穿插啲真實嘅歷史事件，內戰、打仗、恐怖分子抬頭等等，睇完你會有好深感受。"}]}